name: Take a Chance
description:
We hook up with 3 local artist to make Pop Haul NFT Merchandise.
Introduce Ronas, Java born and raised Graffiti Artist from the Manhood Crew also actively contributed on Cluster of Molding Daedal graffiti collective.

Artwork Info

Artist : Ronas 
Project Name : Take a Chance
Year : 2021

Each NFT has underlying physical real trading cards.
Everytime you buy this NFT you’ll also get Numbered Printed Version of each Artworks.
Pop Haul is an Event and Store located in Indonesia.
This Logo created by Ainal.R for Pop Haul NFT.
